Title: Canonical and D-transformations in Theories with Constraints

Comments: 16 pages, LaTeX

Journal-ref: Int.J.Theor.Phys. 35 (1996) 87-99

A class class of transformations in a super phase space (we call themD-transformations) is described, which play in theories with second-classconstraints the role of ordinary canonical transformations in theories withoutconstraints.